LZ WS2024 Experiment Attribution
==================================

This overlay implements the LUX-ZEPLIN (LZ) WIMP-search result from the
2024 WIMP-search data release.

Citation
--------
LZ Collaboration, "First Dark Matter Search Results from the LUX-ZEPLIN
(LZ) Experiment," Phys. Rev. Lett. (PRL) 131, 041002 (2023);
arXiv:2207.03764.

LZ Collaboration, "New results on WIMP dark matter from LZ," arXiv:2410.17036
(2024, LZ WS2024 dataset).

Data provenance
---------------
Efficiency tables and background distributions are derived from publicly
available data in the LZ papers cited above (LZ Collaboration, licensed
under the LZ publication policy for scientific data).

The DDCalc Fortran module implementing this experiment follows the DDCalc
module pattern (Bringmann et al., EPJC 2021, arXiv:2103.04039) and is
authored by the hephaestus DDCalc overlay team.

Status: STUB — efficiency table and Fortran module are placeholders.
Real data arrives at v1.1 overlay publication.
